name: WiR @ Apex.AI
description:
Celebrate Ada Lovelace Day with Women in Robotics and Apex.AI

The Future of Mobility is Software Defined. We are hosting an in-person event with networking, refreshments, and a presentation with Q&A in our headquarters - an iconic historical building in Palo Alto on October 11 from 6 to 8 pm PST. 
RSVP today! HERE OR HERE




Performance Test: A latency and performance testing tool for ROS 2 middleware
with Divya Agarwal
ROS 2 is a rather heterogeneous and complex system that depends on several components. Recently we have seen multiple attempts to create performance reports in ROS 2 that were plainly incorrect or largely incomplete. In this talk, we first explain the terminology relevant for performance testing, emphasizing the parameters that influence the performance of ROS 2 the most.

name: WiR Organizers & Volunteers Get Together
description:
If you're helping Women in Robotics or interested in volunteering then this meeting is for you. 
Let's create more local chapters and events, more online activities, more stories and inspiring content. Bring your ideas, your enthusiasm and your questions.
